      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so there isn't a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
