    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its visceral driving dynamics. This example features the legendary S54B32 power unit, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double VANOS system. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise shifts, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically flawless, the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and rod bearings were replaced with OEM+ components to ensure long-term reliability. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, offering the signature communicative feedback this chassis is known for. Finished in pristine original paint with a flawless interior, this is a turn-key enthusiast piece.",
